    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129205_37_732-818",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "732-818",
      "markText": "崇拜是把自己掏空了，交给人家。如果人家拿过去随手一扔，或在人家手里丢失了，你呢？你就光剩下一个空壳，整个完了！人生是一次性的。你便永远像个空纸盒那样被遗落在世上，无法挽回。",
      "totalCount": 1802,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129205&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=732&rangeEnd=818",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4bd32c90813ab98f8g015aee?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=732&rangeEnd=818"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300129205_38_3039-3087",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "3039-3087",
      "markText": "那时我们决不会认为是在迫害人，相反觉得我们很英雄，很正义，立场坚定。这便是当时学生们的自我感觉。",
      "totalCount": 1615,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300129205&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=3039&rangeEnd=3087",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4bd32c90813ab98f8g015aee?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=3039&rangeEnd=3087"
    },
